{"tid":622474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(馬來西亞) 穆斯林學生舉辦「防同性戀」比賽, 引公憤","createTime":"2018-04-09T07:16:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-10T13:01:39.000Z","uid":134071,"like":20,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"76c411811abcc34684579b9416018404df3aa700","tid":622474,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T07:16:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"http://www.chinapress.com.my/20180404/%E8%BE%A6%E9%98%B2%E5%90%8C%E6%80%A7%E6%88%80%E6%AF%94%E8%B3%BD-%E7%A9%86%E6%96%AF%E6%9E%97%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E5%8D%94%E6%9C%83%E5%BC%95%E5%85%AC%E6%86%A4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinapress.com.my%2F20180404%2F%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E9%2598%25B2%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%2580%25A7%25E6%2588%2580%25E6%25AF%2594%25E8%25B3%25BD-%25E7%25A9%2586%25E6%2596%25AF%25E6%259E%2597%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%258D%2594%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25BC%2595%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%2586%25A4%2F&d=zzcAzgRpBJJpPIykeAO1UwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=0eecc669\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinapress.com.my/20180404/%E8%BE%A6%E9%98%B2%E5%90%8C%E6%80%A7%E6%88%80%E6%AF%94%E8%B3%BD-%E7%A9%86%E6%96%AF%E6%9E%97%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E5%8D%94%E6%9C%83%E5%BC%95%E5%85%AC%E6%86%A4/</a></span><br />\n<br />\n辦&ldquo;防同性戀&rdquo;比賽 穆斯林學生協會引公憤<br />\n2018年4月04日<br />\n（圖／路透社）（圖／路透社）<br />\n（吉隆坡4日訊）搞創意？有大學因主辦讓同性戀學生&ldquo;轉換&rdquo;，協助他們返回正軌的比賽，結果卻引發憤怒，被指不尊重男女同性戀、雙性戀和跨性別者（LGBT）的權益。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;法新社&rdquo;報導指出，社會活躍分子警告說，此類比賽可能會驅使以穆斯林佔多數的大馬社會的自殺傾向。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>這項比賽日前由穆斯林學生協會在理大（USM）舉辦，比賽徵求參與者創作&ldquo;防止同性戀&rdquo;的視頻和海報，主辦方指這是協助學生&ldquo;回歸自然&rdquo;運動的一部分。</strong><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;法新社&rdquo;引述一名穆斯林學生協會會員阿米拉（22歲）說，比賽旨在協助男女同性戀、雙性戀和跨性別者返回正軌，並形容這是一種&ldquo;軟性方法&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我們將努力改變它們，男女同性戀、雙性戀和跨性別者就像吸煙，它對健康有害。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我們希望與男女同性戀、雙性戀和跨性別者接觸，並通過伊斯蘭教義影響他們。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n去年，衛生部公開在網站上舉辦影片競賽，徵求如何&ldquo;預防&rdquo;同性戀和跨性別的影片，也引發LGBT團體不滿，批評政府帶頭歧視LGBT族群。"},{"pid":"f0a1489e4ada2d1c47661ea44f008816a6fce2d5","tid":622474,"uid":36857,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T07:18:26.000Z","msg":"穆斯林 vs LGBT<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n世界大戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a07e75e9298b137b9a0ca5b54fa37e364890ae0","tid":622474,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T07:27:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b186627d73b764fddee35b7e338ad0ed1a76b425","tid":622474,"uid":60545,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T07:32:08.000Z","msg":"垃圾國家"},{"pid":"a85341b2a9020623b267079e3ca0e02de0122fff","tid":622474,"uid":34223,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T07:32:13.000Z","msg":"Muslim 根本就係人類文明最大嘅敵人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94e2710bf480198b270eafa3da8f6f7c55308908","tid":622474,"uid":174601,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T07:33:21.000Z","msg":"有啲係後天既<br />\n但係90%基佬都係天生囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"823ce4020052b05f5b943babfcdd736d8235f54c","tid":622474,"uid":12853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T07:33:52.000Z","msg":"再挑埋女膠<br />\n左膠大戰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3740ba23a267b9cc810ed3cf478c160d534db07a","tid":622474,"uid":69794,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b186627d73b764fddee35b7e338ad0ed1a76b425","tid":622474,"uid":60545,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T07:32:08.000Z","msg":"垃圾國家"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T07:34:23.000Z","msg":"垃圾宗教<